    MaterialsList
    A MaterialsList is a PersistentList that stores an abstract set of block or item materials.
    MaterialsListener
    A MaterialsListener is a Listener that listens for inventory clicks and crafting, and determines if the given event should be blocked due to banned materials being used.
    MaterialsListener.ScheduledInventoryCheck
    A ScheduledInventoryCheck is constructed with any given InventoryClickEvent.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Executables
    The Executables interface represents the set of commands supported by this plugin, and contains an executable object for each command that acts as the main procedure for the command.
    Rules
    The Rules interface represents the set of commands supported by this plugin, and contains a CommandRulesEntry for each command, which defines information about the expected context of the command.
